# Truth machine in Nook.
# Truth machine is a machine where:
# You get an input from the user
# If input is 0: Print 0
# If input is 1:
# 	Repeat infinitely:
#			Print 1
# For more, see:
# https://esolangs.org/wiki/Truth-machine
i # Get user's input
{0 =} # Condition
{0 w} # Then
{[][1 w]t} # Else
? # If
